WEBVTT

00:13:28.720 --> 00:13:30.936
And I hear people say things like,

00:13:30.960 --> 00:13:34.096
"Well, OK, but why don't we just do

00:13:34.120 --> 00:13:36.576
a Friday afternoon
ping-pong tournament instead?

00:13:36.600 --> 00:13:37.920
That will be way more fun."

00:13:38.720 --> 00:13:40.296
What do you say to those people?

00:13:40.320 --> 00:13:42.696
DC: Well, they're right,
it would be way more fun.

00:13:42.720 --> 00:13:44.096
It would be incredibly fun.

00:13:44.120 --> 00:13:48.896
It would be a type of engagement
that is delightful.

00:13:48.920 --> 00:13:51.616
The only problem is you can't
just have that kind of fun.

00:13:51.640 --> 00:13:53.736
You know, fun comes in different flavors.

00:13:53.760 --> 00:13:57.656
There's shallow fun, which is
having that ping-pong tournament,

00:13:57.680 --> 00:13:59.896
going out and having a blast together.

00:13:59.920 --> 00:14:02.056
That's wonderful,
but that kind of wears off.